# STUDENT ML PROJECT BEST PRACTICE NOTE:
# Typically, datasets and trained models shouldn't be pushed to GitHub 
# if they are massive (e.g., >100MB).
# However, since this is a final academic project, graders and reviewers 
# often need the data (~11MB) and model (~2MB) to easily run the system 
# without complex setup steps. 
